# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:13
translate chinese julianas7_e2b25c7e:

    # bn "No, my parents died very shortly after I was born."
    bn "不，我父母在我出生后不久就去世了。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:14
translate chinese julianas7_513c5cad:

    # bn "I think they wanted more children, but they did not have time to make them."
    bn "我想他们原本还想要更多孩子，但没来得及生。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:15
translate chinese julianas7_9c1677e2:

    # bn "If they wouldn't have died, I think they would have had a big family and I would probably be a very different person."
    bn "如果他们没去世，我想家里会很热闹，而我大概也会是截然不同的人。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:16
translate chinese julianas7_256d4fae:

    # pc "Oh, I'm sorry, Juliana."
    pc "哦，真抱歉，朱莉安娜。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:18
translate chinese julianas7_c7d8288e:

    # bn "No, it's okay."
    bn "不，没关系。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:19
translate chinese julianas7_d4f4947d:

    # bn "Dang, I'm sorry. I didn't mean to bring the mood down. I know I can do that sometimes."
    bn "天哪，真对不起。我不是故意要扫兴的。我知道自己有时会这样。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:21
translate chinese julianas7_af993d33:

    # bn "I think me not having any siblings is part of why I'm so awkward with people."
    bn "我觉得我没有兄弟姐妹，也是我跟人相处这么笨拙的原因之一。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:22
translate chinese julianas7_47df8345:

    # bn "I never really had anybody to talk to growing up, except for my grandmother and her friends from church."
    bn "我长大后真的没什么人可以倾诉，除了我奶奶和她教会里的朋友。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:23
translate chinese julianas7_deaf570a:

    # bn "I don't even have any cousins or anything. My mom was my grandmother's only child."
    bn "我甚至没有表亲之类的。我妈妈是我奶奶的独生女。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:24
translate chinese julianas7_e5847b85:

    # bn "So I was never around people my own age."
    bn "所以我从来没和同龄人待在一起过。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:25
translate chinese julianas7_7994ab07:

    # pc "But you had friends at school, right?"
    pc "但你在学校有朋友吧？"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:27
translate chinese julianas7_14d5379b:

    # bn "I've made a few friends, but it hasn't been easy, and my best friend moved away to go to college after high school."
    bn "我交过几个朋友，但这并不容易，而且我最好的朋友高中毕业后就搬走了去上大学。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:28
translate chinese julianas7_4a326c2b:

    # bn "I just get so nervous around people. They think I'm weird."
    bn "我一跟人在一起就特别紧张。他们觉得我很怪。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:29
translate chinese julianas7_32194466:

    # bn "So I mostly just read my books alone."
    bn "所以我大多时候都独自看书。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:30
translate chinese julianas7_2b8e19d5:

    # pc "It sounds pretty lonely."
    pc "听起来挺孤独的。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:32
translate chinese julianas7_42a9a832:

    # bn "Sometimes it can be, but most of the time I like being alone. It's comfortable."
    bn "有时候确实如此，但大多数时候我喜欢独处。这样很自在。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:34
translate chinese julianas7_efd6e210:

    # bn "Being with you is pretty comfortable too though."
    bn "不过和你在一起也很自在。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:35
translate chinese julianas7_944c5d83:

    # bn "Comfortable and exciting at the same time."
    bn "既自在又令人兴奋。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:36
translate chinese julianas7_5b2ccbcd:

    # pc "I'm glad you're comfortable around me."
    pc "很高兴你和我在一起时感到自在。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:37
translate chinese julianas7_94b97139:

    # pc "And I don't think you're weird at all."
    pc "而且我一点也不觉得你奇怪。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:39
translate chinese julianas7_36e3b0fa:

    # bn "Really? I know I can be awkward sometimes."
    bn "真的吗？我知道自己有时候会有点笨拙。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:40
translate chinese julianas7_64237c98:

    # pc "Sometimes. But your awkwardness is cute. Never weird."
    pc "有时候吧。不过你那点笨拙的样子挺可爱的，从来不会让人觉得怪怪的。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaConversations/julianas7.rpy:42
translate chinese julianas7_53ddd9f6:

    # bn "Thanks, [pcname]."
    bn "谢谢，[pcname]。"

